      "content": "hey, i just landed in dubai after a really long flight from london and im feeling kinda weird. my chest kind of hurts when i breathe in deep and im having a hard time catching my breath. i think im just super stressed from the travel and maybe having a bit of a panic attack... do u think that's what it is? it's making me feel really anxious.",
