    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i dont really want to make a big scene at the airport if i dont have to. it's probably just the caffeine and the jet lag making my heart race. it's just a sharp little poke when i breathe, not like a heart attack or anything. u think i can just go back to my hotel, take some ibuprofen, and sleep it off? i dont want to waste an ambulance on just anxiety.",
